he JDK’s `jdk.attach.jmod`.\n- Adds a test `AttachProvider`/`VirtualMachine` implementation into that temporary `tools.jar`.\n- Points JOL’s legacy `java.home/../lib/tools.jar` lookup at the temporary JDK layout.\n- Exercises the public JOL path via `ClassLayout.toPrintable()` and `VMSupport.sizeOf(...)`.\n- Keeps Native Image dynamic class-loading handling via `NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(...)`.\n\nThis should allow `InstrumentationSupport.tryDynamicAttach()` to progress past the initial `VirtualMachine` class lookup and exercise the reflective attach/load/detach/resource call sites through JOL’s normal public API entry points.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_009820b8aefa0f84016a2437427da08196b39429dbb6a52fd8\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1869, "output": 979, "cacheRead": 53760, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 56608, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1780758317327, "responseId": "resp_009820b8aefa0f84016a24372de640819681f3028e18edae12"}}
